name: Courage Of A Skywalker (V)
Lore: 'Despite being alone, trapped and desperately outmatched, Luke continued his battle with the Dark Lord of the Sith.',
Text: 'During battle, unless Inner Strength on table, initiate a duel between your participating Skywalker (except Shmi) present and a participating Dark Jedi present. Both players draw two destiny and add ability. Higher total wins. Loser is lost.',
